org.dgfoundation.amp.nireports.schema

Interface NiReportsSchema

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractReportsSchema, AmpReportsSchema, DRCReportsTestSchema, HardcodedReportsTestSchema, TanzaniaReportsTestSchema, TestcasesReportsSchema

    public interface NiReportsSchema
    an interface describing the Schema of an API's reporting needs. For a detailed reading about defining and using a schema, please refer to https://wiki.dgfoundation.org/display/AMPDOC/2.+NiReports+Configuration%3A+the+schema
